OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FBird lovers could see golden eagles
OL,7,Freturn to England, the Government has
OL,8,Fsaid, as it announced new funding to
OL,9,Fexplore their reintroduction.
OL,11,FMentioned more than 40 times in
OL,12,FShakespeare's work, the bird of prey
OL,13,Fhas a huge two-metre wingspan and
OL,14,Fplays a vital role in keeping the
OL,15,Fwhole ecosystem in balance as an apex
OL,16,Fpredator.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
