OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775952175
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FThe species was once widespread across
OL,7,FEngland, but it was virtually wiped
OL,8,Fout by sheep farmers and gamekeepers
OL,9,Fin the Victorian era, who viewed them
OL,10,Fas a threat to lambs and game birds,
OL,11,Fcompounded by 20th-century pesticide
OL,12,Fuse affecting their fertility.
OL,14,FOnly a handful of pairs have been seen
OL,15,Fin England in the last 150 years, with
OL,16,Fthe last eagle dying in the Lake
OL,17,FDistrict in 2016, though they are
OL,18,Fstill found in Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
