OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775952175
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FThis could include reintroduction
OL,7,Fefforts that would see juveniles aged
OL,8,Fsix to eight weeks old released as
OL,9,Fearly as next year.
OL,11,FMs Reynolds said: "This government is
OL,12,Fcommitted to protecting and restoring
OL,13,Four most threatened native wildlife `
OL,14,Fand that includes bringing back iconic
OL,15,Fspecies like the golden eagle.
OL,17,F"Backed by #1 million of government
OL,18,Ffunding ` we will work alongside
OL,19,Fpartners and communities to make the
OL,20,Fgolden eagle a feature of English
OL,21,Flandscapes once again."
OL,26,@sD@SOUyD@AOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
