OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775952175
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FIn Southern Scotland, golden eagle
OL,7,Fpopulations have recovered to record
OL,8,Fnumbers because of a major project to
OL,9,Frestore their populations in the area.
OL,11,FSatellite tracking indicates that some
OL,12,Fof these translocated birds have
OL,13,Falready begun to fly across the border
OL,14,Fand explore northern England, the
OL,15,FGovernment said.
OL,17,FIt is hoped the new funding will help
OL,18,Fto support these birds in England,
OL,19,Fcoupled with targeted reintroductions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
