OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775952175
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FForestry England's research found that
OL,7,FScottish birds could be seen across
OL,8,Fnorthern England within 10 years, but
OL,9,Fit will take longer for breeding
OL,10,Fgolden eagles to become established in
OL,11,FEngland.
OL,13,FMike Seddon, Forestry England chief
OL,14,Fexecutive, said: "The detailed
OL,15,Ffindings of our feasibility study will
OL,16,Fguide us with our partners, Restoring
OL,17,FUpland Nature, to take the next steps
OL,18,Fto explore the recovery of golden
OL,19,Feagles in northern England.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
