OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775952175
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,F"This (Environment Department) funding
OL,7,Fmeans we can build on the good work we
OL,8,Fhave begun, taking the time to build
OL,9,Fsupport and engage with local
OL,10,Fcommunities, landowners and land
OL,11,Fmanagers and conservation
OL,12,Forganisations."
OL,14,FMinisters said the charity Restoring
OL,15,FUpland Nature (RUN) will lead the new
OL,16,Fproject alongside other partners,
OL,17,Fincluding Forestry England, seeking to
OL,18,Freplicate the success of the south of
OL,19,FScotland project.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@OO]
