OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775952175
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FCat Barlow, RUN chief executive, said:
OL,7,F"This presents a truly exciting and
OL,8,Fpotentially game-changing moment for
OL,9,Fthe return of golden eagles to
OL,10,FNorthern England.
OL,12,F"Our priority will be to listen, to
OL,13,Fwork in partnership, and to ensure
OL,14,Fthat golden eagle recovery supports
OL,15,Fboth nature and the people who manage
OL,16,Fthese landscapes, so that everyone can
OL,17,Fenjoy the thrill of seeing golden
OL,18,Feagles flying high once again across
OL,19,Fthe uplands of the UK."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU{D@WO]
