OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775952175
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FThe funding comes as part of the #60
OL,7,Fmillion in species recovery funding
OL,8,Fannounced by the Environment
OL,9,FDepartment last week.
OL,11,FIt ties into work aimed at meeting the
OL,12,FUK's legally binding target to halt
OL,13,Fthe decline in species abundance by
OL,14,F2030 and reduce species extinction
OL,15,Frisk by 2042 against 2022 levels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
